# Historical Issue Regression Pipeline (STRICT)

> Authority: `historical-issue-regression` skill (`/home/charles2/.ssh/.cursor/skills/historical-issue-regression/SKILL.md`)
> Master: `restaurant-voice-agent.mdc`. **Skipping any step invalidates the fix.**

## Protocol

After every implementation fix or new feature — after DEPLOY VERIFICATION and before claiming success — the agent MUST run the `historical-issue-regression` skill checks in order and produce the REGRESSION REPORT block.

### Mandatory Checks (in order)

| # | Check | Gate |
|---|-------|------|
| 1 | Clear stale `__pycache__` | Zero dirs remaining |
| 2 | Semantic search for past-bug pattern recurrence (5 queries) | No past-bug class detected |
| 3 | State shape consistency (`test_state_shape_consistency.py`) | All tests pass |
| 4 | FSM unit tests (`test_conversation_fsm.py`) | 65/65 both tenants |
| 5 | Dead code / cleanliness sweep | No `__pycache__`, no keyword/regex, no stale callers |
| 6 | Environment compatibility | `v4_pipeline_clean.py` >1000 lines, FSM import OK, health OK |
| 7 | Past transcript cross-reference (SemanticSearch) | No regressing issue detected |

See the skill file for exact commands, PASS/FAIL criteria, and per-check ACTION items.

### REGRESSION REPORT (mandatory block)

At the end of every implementation response, after DEPLOY VERIFICATION, the agent MUST output:

```
REGRESSION REPORT
- SemSearch (past-bug patterns): [PASS / FAIL]
- State shape consistency:       [PASS / FAIL]
- FSM unit tests:                [PASS X/Y / FAIL]
- Dead code / cleanliness:       [PASS / FAIL]
  - __pycache__ cleared:         [YES / NO]
  - Keyword/regex violations:    [NONE / FOUND]
  - Deleted-method callers:      [NONE / FOUND]
- Environment compatibility:     [PASS / FAIL]
  - v4_pipeline_clean lines:     [count]
  - FSM import:                  [OK / FAIL]
  - Health endpoint:             [OK / FAIL]
- Transcript cross-reference:    [PASS / FAIL]
- OVERALL:                       [PASS / FAIL]
```

**If OVERALL is FAIL, the agent MUST fix the failing checks before claiming the change is complete.**

## Hard Stops

| Condition | Verdict |
|-----------|---------|
| State shape consistency fails | **BLOCKER** — fix field name, never weaken test (KI-031 class) |
| FSM unit tests <65/65 | **BLOCKER** — FSM is core authority, no regression allowed |
| Keyword/regex intent code found in `server/brain/` | **BLOCKER** — cite Pure LLM Intent rule, remove immediately |
| `v4_pipeline_clean.py` empty or <1000 lines | **BLOCKER** — production pipeline is broken |
| Health endpoint fails after restart | **BLOCKER** — server is not serving, check `journalctl` |
| Semantic search detects past-bug pattern recurrence | **BLOCKER** — cite BREAKTHROUGH RULE, revert or fix |
| Remaining callers of deleted method | **BLOCKER** — stale references cause runtime crashes |
| Transcript cross-reference finds known regressing issue | **BLOCKER** — revisit past resolution before proceeding |
| OVERALL is FAIL | **BLOCKER** — do not claim success, enumerate failures |

